{"tid":2013190,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"屯門珀御1房戶「鬆綁」即沽 3年升值17%","createTime":"2020-05-12T06:51:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-16T14:27:05.000Z","uid":160028,"like":12,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"41c712d5bf328154779a364e3c883228100a8819","tid":2013190,"uid":160028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T06:51:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://ps.hket.com/article/2640830?r=cpstni\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fps.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2640830%3Fr%3Dcpstni&d=EvsgW2mpOVZdTd1tTx%2BWmMtNvD6oN5AbUd1%2F%2Bp%2BoAYU%3D&h=68524c47\" target=\"_blank\">https://ps.hket.com/article/2640830?r=cpstni</a><br />\n<br />\n中原地產屯門兆康站分行資深分區營業經理劉月華表示，一二手持續升溫，成交急速。屯門珀御剛錄得SSD「鬆綁」即沽的成交個案，單位為高層B室，實用面積354平方呎，一房間隔，向南，開價598萬元，新近獲外區首置客垂青，議價後以570萬元承接，平均實用呎價16102元。<br />\n<br />\n劉月華表示，買家睇樓約1星期，鍾情珀御樓齡新，上址間隔合用，樓價合預算，快速拍板入市。原業主則於2017年5月以488.15萬元一手買入單位，剛SSD「鬆綁」，現沽出單位，賬面獲利81.85萬元，單位期內升值約17%。<br />\n<br />\n下年所有一房入場費20000呎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17c57d6c96d381922b14c4fb74842109b6490a56","tid":2013190,"uid":38170,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":8,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T06:55:42.000Z","msg":"扣埋物業稅同佣<br />\n帳面賺得60萬都無"},{"pid":"abf082100ae77048ab55c0260fe0ad08f9fcaa23","tid":2013190,"uid":44243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T07:02:30.000Z","msg":"如果無5成首期以上 根本無肉食"},{"pid":"3d0a7d3a1a62476739e2c1cf866bf2bd6f7a5b3d","tid":2013190,"uid":13165,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"quote":{"pid":"17c57d6c96d381922b14c4fb74842109b6490a56","tid":2013190,"uid":38170,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":8,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T06:55:42.000Z","msg":"扣埋物業稅同佣<br />\n帳面賺得60萬都無"},"citedBy":1,"reply